description: Lists the deployment configurations with the user or Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: deploymentConfigsList
nested_items.description: A list of deployment configurations, including built-in configurations such as CodeDeployDefault.OneAtATime.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If a large amount of information is returned, an identifier is also returned. It can be used in a subsequent list deployment configurations call to return the next set of deployment configurations in the list.
